      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Older vehicle in poor overall condition and priced accordingly. It shows heavy wear inside and out, with noticeable cosmetic flaws, an aged interior, and buyers should expect mechanical issues and deferred maintenance. This is not a clean or well-sorted example, but it could suit someone looking for a budget project, parts vehicle, or basic transportation with realistic expectations.",
