    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Practical, affordable, and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers a great opportunity for anyone seeking dependable basic transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age cosmetically, but it delivers strong value for buyers who prioritize utility, everyday convenience, and low upfront cost. A smart choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone needing an inexpensive extra vehicle.",
