      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone handy, a first project, or just a cheap runaround. It\u2019s being advertised honestly and priced with its condition in mind, so you know exactly what kind of opportunity you\u2019re getting. If you want something straightforward, approachable, and worth a look, this could be a really good fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with solid bones and plenty of usable life left. The powertrain pulls cleanly, the transmission does its job well, and the chassis still feels composed enough to be a great budget commuter, work car, or weekend project. It shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but that also means you can drive it without worry while benefiting from a straightforward, easy-to-own setup. A practical entry point for someone who wants dependable mechanical fundamentals at an accessible price.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
