      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward value for someone seeking dependable basic transportation or a practical project. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a solid opportunity at an accessible price point for a buyer who appreciates honest, affordable motoring.",
