      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great if you need simple transport, a backup vehicle, or something to tinker with on the weekends. Priced fairly for what it is, and being sold by someone who believes in being upfront and easy to deal with.",
